questions.questionText: Upload the following 4 Registration Images
Is there any evidence of major or hail damage to the car?
Has the chassis or cab structure been modified in any way?
Is there any evidence of flood damage to the vehicle?
Is there any evidence of fire damage to the vehicle?
Is the OBD II (On-Board Diagnostics) system functioning properly and free of error codes?
What is the overall exterior and interior condition of the vehicle?
Are the seats in good condition?
Do all seat adjustment mechanisms (manual or electric) function properly in all directions?
Does the seat slide smoothly along the adjustment rail and lock securely in each position?
Are all seat belts in good condition, functioning properly?
Are all interior trim pieces (dash panels, door trims, moldings, etc.) secure, clean, and free from damage?
Is the radio/multimedia system working properly, including power, sound, tuning, and all inputs (Bluetooth, USB, AUX)?
Are all speakers working properly with clear sound and no distortion?
Is the rear window demister functioning properly and clearing the window effectively?
Is the air conditioner and heater working properly, providing effective cooling and heating?
Are the windshield washers and wipers functioning properly and effectively clearing the windshield?
Is the horn working properly and producing a clear sound?
Do all doors, locks, and hinges operate smoothly and securely without damage?
Is the inside door handle functioning properly and securely attached?
Are the weather strips intact, properly sealed, and free from cracks or damage?
Do all windows operate smoothly and fully open and close without issues?
Are all dash warning lights and gauges functioning correctly without any persistent alerts?
Is the OBD II system functioning properly with no active fault codes?
Are all interior and exterior lights functioning properly without any faults?
Is the owner’s manual available and are the service intervals up to date?
Is there any unusual odor or other issues inside the vehicle?
Upload the following 3   Images
Is the front bumper securely attached and free from dents or cracks?
Is the front side member (right) free from damage, rust, or deformation?
Is the front side member (left) free from damage, rust, or deformation?
Is the front grill securely attached and free from damage or excessive wear?
Is the radiator core support free from damage, rust, or signs of previous repair?
Is the bonnet properly aligned, free from dents or rust, and functioning correctly?
Is the cowl panel and firewall free from damage, rust, or signs of structural repair?
Is the windshield free from cracks, chips, and signs of leakage or improper installation?
Is the roof free from dents, rust, or signs of previous repair or damage?
Is the sunroof or convertible top fully functional and in good cosmetic condition, without leaks or damage?
Is the right front wing free from dents, rust, and signs of previous damage or repair?
Is the right front door free from damage, rust, and properly aligned with smooth opening and closing?
Is the right rearview mirror securely mounted, functional, and free from cracks or damage?
Is there any visible damage or dent on the right rear door?
Is there any dent, scratch observed on the right sliding door?
Is there any dent, scratch on the right rear wing?

Is there any dent, scratch, rust on the Left Front Wing?

Is the Left Rocker Panel free from dents, rust, scratches, or any visible damage?

Is the Rear Screen (rear windshield) free from cracks, chips, scratches, or signs of replacement?
Is the Rear Bumper free from dents, scratches, cracks, or misalignment?
Is the Rear Side Member (Right) free from dents, rust, structural damage, or signs of repair?
Is the Rear Side Member (Left) free from dents, rust, structural damage, or signs of repair?
Is the Right A-Pillar free from dents, rust, cracks, or signs of structural repair?
Is the Right B-Pillar free from dents, rust, cracks, or signs of structural repair?
Is the Right C-Pillar free from dents, rust, cracks, or signs of structural repair?
Is the Right D-Pillar free from dents, rust, cracks, or signs of structural repair?
Is the Left A-Pillar free from dents, rust, cracks, or signs of structural repair?
Is the Left B-Pillar free from dents, rust, cracks, or signs of structural repair?
Is the Left C-Pillar free from dents, rust, cracks, or signs of structural repair?
Is the Left D-Pillar free from dents, rust, cracks, or signs of structural repair?
Are the Chassis Frames & Members visibly free from rust, bends, cracks, or signs of accident damage or repair?
Is the Underbody and its components free from rust, oil leaks, damage, or signs of impact or repair?
Is the Front Suspension visibly free from damage, leakage, rust, or any signs of wear or misalignment?
Is the Rear Suspension visibly free from damage, leakage, rust, or any signs of wear or misalignment?
Are the Steering Components visibly free from damage, wear, leaks, or signs of rust or misalignment?
Is the Transmission Housing free from visible cracks, oil leaks, rust, or signs of impact or repair?
Is the Exhaust system free from visible rust, damage, leaks, or unusual noise indications?
Is the Differential free from visible oil leaks, rust, damage, or unusual noise during movement?
Are the Drive Shafts free from visible damage, cracks, rust, or leakage from boots or joints?
Are all door handles present, securely fitted, and functioning properly without any damage or looseness?
Is the Fuel Cap present, undamaged, and opening and closing properly without any leakage?
Is the Spare Tire Housing intact, securely mounted, and free from rust, damage, or missing parts?

Is there any visible oil, coolant, or fluid leak in the engine bay area?
Does the engine start smoothly without any delay, cranking struggle, or abnormal noise?
Does the key turn smoothly or the push start function operate normally without any delay or malfunction?
Does the engine idle smoothly without abnormal vibrations, shaking, or fluctuating RPM?
Is the engine bay free from any squeaking noises during startup or while idling?
Is the exhaust system quiet during operation and free from any visible leaks or unusual noises?
Is there any white or black smoke emitted from the exhaust during engine start or acceleration?
Are the Chassis Frames & Members in the engine bay free from rust, cracks, damage, or signs of repair?
Are all essential fluid levels (engine oil, coolant, brake fluid, washer fluid) at the correct level and free from contamination?
Are there any visible fluid leaks (oil, coolant, brake, or transmission) in the engine bay area?
Are the engine and transmission mountings secure, free from cracks, damage, or excessive wear?
Are all hoses and pipes in the engine bay securely connected, free from cracks, leaks, or visible wear?
Are the water pump, hoses, and cooling fan in good condition, properly functioning, and free from leaks or damage?
Is the ignition system functioning properly, with no visible damage to coils, wires, or spark plugs?
Is the fuel system free from leaks, corrosion, or damage, and are all connections secure and functioning properly?
Is the radiator and its cap in good condition, free from leaks, rust, or damage, and securely fitted?
Are the drive belt and pulleys in good condition, properly aligned, and free from cracks, fraying, or unusual noise?
Is the brake booster functioning properly and free from visible damage, corrosion, or vacuum leaks?
Is the brake master cylinder maintaining proper pressure and free from leaks, cracks, or fluid loss?
Is the battery free from leaks, and is the battery support bracket clean and free from corrosion or damage?
Does the battery pass the voltage and load test, indicating good health and proper charging capacity?
Are the tires in good condition, with no damage and a valid manufacturing year?
Are the wheel rims free from dents, cracks, rust, or visible damage?
Is the spare tire and rim present, in good condition, and free from damage or excessive wear?
Are the brake hoses, calipers, and pipes free from leaks, cracks, rust, or visible damage?
Are the front and rear brake pads in good condition with sufficient thickness and no uneven wear?
Are the front and rear brake discs free from cracks, warping, excessive wear, or rust?
Are the brake drums and related components free from any fluid leakage, cracks, or visible damage?
Is the parking brake functioning properly and holding the vehicle securely?
Does the battery pass the voltage and load test, indicating good health and proper charging capacity?
